          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1578321209400-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1578321209400-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1578321209400-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1578321209400-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is in the oven, peel and roughly chop your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> into small pieces</p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1578321214973-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1578321214973-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1578321214973-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1578321214973-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1578321214973-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped basil</strong>,<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>cheddar cheese pieces</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> (alternatively, use a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong>)</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> of your<strong> red wine vinegar </strong>(save the rest for later!) with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Blitz together to form a coarse paste – this is your <strong>cheddar pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
