      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything is almost cooked, add your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> to a separate baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until hot and crusty</p><p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>remaining red wine vinegar</strong> with drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1578321230027-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1578321230027-x400.jpg",
